      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with all the plans and the spark—actually died a long time ago. i'm just performing the motions of being alive now. like i'm just a ghost inhabiting a body that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
